1. Project Overview
    1. User actions - authentication,checking balance, depositing money,
     withdraw money, view transactions

Design:
1. main() -> program starts
2. verify pin
    1. pin correct -> menu()
    2. incorrect pin -> give 3 chances to enter correct pin
    3. exit the program if 3 chances are completed
3. menu()
    1. ask choice
    2. every choice will have a separate function
